question: Tell me about yourself.
answer:
AI Assistant Overview and Capabilities
tell me about your self
Hi! I'm DeepSeek Chat, an AI assistant created by DeepSeek to help answer your questions, provide insights, and assist with a wide range of topics—from general knowledge and coding to creative writing and productivity tips.

🔹 About Me:
Free to Use: Currently, I’m completely free with no hidden costs!

Knowledgeable: My training data goes up to July 2024, so I’m well-informed on many topics.

Large Context Handling: I can process up to 128K tokens, meaning I can remember and analyze long conversations or documents.

Multilingual: I can understand and respond in multiple languages.

File Support: You can upload PDFs, Word docs, Excel sheets, PPTs, and more, and I’ll help extract and analyze the content.

No Internet Access (by default): I don’t browse the web unless you enable "web search" for real-time info.

🔹 What I Can Do for You:
✔ Answer general knowledge & trivia questions
✔ Help with coding, debugging, and explanations
✔ Assist in writing (essays, stories, emails, resumes)
✔ Explain complex topics in simple terms
✔ Analyze uploaded documents
✔ Offer productivity & study tips

Want to test my abilities? Ask me anything!

tone.feedback: Your tone is positive and enthusiastic, which is great for an interview. Keep up the energy! However, be careful not to come across as overly enthusiastic as it might seem insincere.

word_choice.feedback: Good use of professional language! Words like created strengthen your responses. Try to reduce filler words/phrases like um, well, so. These can make you sound less confident.

confidence.feedback: You sound reasonably confident. With a few adjustments, you could project even more authority.
